==English==
===Noun===
{{rft|how should the plurals be described?}}
'''antenna'''  (''plural:'' '''[[antennae]]''', '''[[antennas]]''')

# A device to receive or transmit radio signals etc. by converting [[electromagnetic radiation]] into electrical signals.
# A [[feeler]] organ on the head of an [[insect]], [[crab]] or other [[animal]].

